  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to yelp-xsl</title>

    <para>The <application>yelp-xsl</application> package contains XSL stylesheets
    that are used by the yelp help browser to format Docbook and Mallard documents.
    </para>

    &lfs70_checked;

